    </div>

    <div class="mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Can I add online ordering to Durable?</h3>
